videos.description: Following the steal, Florida's Dontay Bassett creates space in the paint and throws down a two-handed slam.
videos.headline: Bassett rocks rim with two-handed slam

videos.description: Florida's Chris Chiozza sends a quick pass over to Egor Koulechov behind the arc for a corner 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Chiozza sets up Koulechov's corner 3

videos.description: Florida's Chris Chiozza dishes to a cutting Jalen Hudson for a loud one-handed finish.
videos.headline: Hudson soars for emphatic one-handed dunk

videos.description: Florida's Kevarrius Hayes tries taking it inside with a layup but is denied by Auburn's Horace Spencer.
videos.headline: Spencer stuffs Hayes in the paint

videos.description: Florida's Chris Chiozza zips a pass inside to Dontay Brissett for an emphatic two-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Chiozza's dime leads to Bassett's slam

videos.description: Auburn's Desean Murray bounces a pass to Mustapha Heron for an easy two-handed finish.
videos.headline: Heron converts two-handed dunk off inbounds pass

videos.description: With the shot clock winding down, Florida's KeVaughn Allen creates space off the dribble to knock down a tough 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Allen displays range on long 3-pointer

videos.description: Florida's KeVaughn Allen launches a near full-court shot and converts to beat the first half buzzer.
videos.headline: Allen sinks ridiculous shot to beat buzzer

videos.description: Auburn's Desean Murray tries finishing with a layup inside but is rejected by Florida's Dontay Bassett.
videos.headline: Bassett rejects Murray inside

videos.description: Auburn's Bryce Brown dishes to a cutting Horace Spencer for a tough finger roll and the foul to earn a chance at a 3-point play.
videos.headline: Spencer converts crafty layup for and-1 chance

videos.description: Florida's Dontay Bassett gets the ball inside and sells a pump fake on a layup attempt to earn the chance at a 3-point play.
videos.headline: Bassett's pump fake leads to and-1 opportunity

videos.description: Horace Spencer finds Mustapha Heron open behind the arc for a 3-pointer late in the second half.
videos.headline: Heron drains corner 3-pointer to give Tigers lead

videos.description: Auburn's Desean Murray backs down his defender and converts a tough layup for a 3-point chance.
videos.headline: Murray finishes tough lay-in for 3-point chance

videos.description: Florida's Chris Chiozza sends a pass inside to Jalen Hudson for a tough lay-in and the foul to earn a chance at a 3-point play.
videos.headline: Hudson sinks clutch layup to give Gators late lead

videos.description: With KeVaughn Allen scoring 24 points and Jalen Hudson adding 19, Florida knocks off No. 12 Auburn 72-66.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Highlight (Florida goes down to the wire to upset Auburn) 2018/02/24 ESHEET

videos.headline: Florida goes down to the wire to upset Auburn
